node.text: Many ask, what was one of the highlights of your first run for office? Without hesitation I say, "My RNC Convention speech". My awesome team stayed up all night to write the best speech I have given to date. Thank you President Trump, the GOP & all those that watched for the opportunity.

node.text: There are only 2100 registered Republicans in the Baltimore City portion of District 7, I received close to 15k votes in the city, tremendous progress. I’m excited to see what the redistricting committee comes up with for the gerrymandered districts in Maryland. Thank you @myone82z_ for making sure we were hitting the streets every single day in Baltimore. The hard work will pay off. Let’s keep our eyes on the prize 🇺🇸

Love today, tomorrow isn’t guaranteed.

node.text:
A great mindset to have @giannis_an34 

For some, humility may never come. Those people will ultimately fail. Block out the noise & focus. Almost a month ago I had some ridiculous accusations thrown at me, but I didn’t let it knock me off my path. My accusers have been silent ever since. Telling a story without an ounce of evidence just to tear another woman down is a bad look on the accuser. Let God handle your light work. Keep going 🇺🇸
